org.rocketproplab.marginalstability.flightcomputer.commands

Class HeartbeatCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rocketproplab.marginalstability.flightcomputer.commands.HeartbeatCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Command

    public class HeartbeatCommand
extends java.lang.Object
implements Command
    This is the Heartbeat Command class that implements the Command interface. The main capabilities of this class includes checking the start time and sending a periodic "heartbeat" signal every second.
    Author:
    Hemanth Battu
